                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-42-off236 t17980912-42-cd237"></join>, a silver tea-pot, value 3l. 10s. and three tea-spoons, value 10s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17980912-42-victim446" type="victimName">
                           Arthur 
                           Anstey
                        <interp inst="t17980912-42-victim446" type="surname" value="Anstey"></interp>
