                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980912-42-victim446 t17980912-42-viclabel238"></join>. and a black silk cloak, value 21s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17980912-42-victim448" type="victimName">
                           Elizabeth 
                           Patey
